## Advantages of working in our company
* good, stable earnings;
* opportunity for career growth;
* paid training;
* young, professional, positive, and friendly team;
* convenient work schedule.
## Why is it worth being a PPC specialist?
A contextual advertising specialist is a person who performs many tasks to create ads to achieve the goal that the customer has set. An expert must create ads in the Google Ads cabinet, analyze the target audience and consider age, gender, region, price per click, and other parameters to reduce advertising costs and increase the flow of customers when setting up ads.## The benefits of cooperating with us
* Constant development and dynamic work. You won’t have to wait long for the first results of your labor. A few months and analysis of advertising campaigns will be enough to understand if your strategy is effective;
* PPC specialists can work in any field of business - from the fashion industry to IT. You can always choose the field you like;
* Specialists have the most significant influence in creating demand among users.
## Our perfect candidate should be able to
* create a contextual advertising launch strategy;
* work with banner and video advertising;
* set up and run advertising campaigns;
* target, quickly retarget promotional campaigns, and select keywords that are as relevant as possible to the product being promoted
* make a list of creative headlines and ads;
* search for the best illustrations for each ad;
* analyze the effectiveness of ads, optimize them and constantly work to increase conversions;
* generate reports;
* create media budgets and media plans.
If you are outgoing, speak English, are responsible for work, have experience as a PPC specialist, and want to develop in this field - leave an application, and we will contact you!
Record a video CV in English, and leave your contacts. Let’s work together.
